# Embedded Python runtime (downloaded by setup-python-env.sh)
# 不带尾斜杠 — 同时捕获目录和误提交的 symlink（曾踩过自指 symlink 的坑）
src-tauri/pyembed

# Embedded Bun runtime (downloaded by setup-bun-runtime.sh)
# gbrain Sprint 2.0 (Path C-2) — bundle Bun binary as Tauri resource.
